#Vapor Snare (#1085) upkeep-cost witness - PARKED, same engine bug as Thirst:
#"all(this) transforms((,newability[upcost[...] sacrifice])) forever" never
#registers its AUpkeep (granted upcost is dead; direct auto=upcost users work).
#Oracle: at my upkeep, sacrifice the snare unless I return a land - with no
#land bounced the snare must go to the graveyard and the bears return to P2.
#The complaint ("sacrificed my creature") matches the OLD bare-upcost form
#which - like all aura auto lines - applied to the ENCHANTED creature.
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
manapool:{4}{U}
hand:vapor snare
library:darksteel citadel,millstone
[PLAYER2]
inplay:grizzly bears
library:darksteel citadel,millstone
[DO]
vapor snare
grizzly bears
goto firstmain
goto firstmain
goto end
goto firstmain
goto end
goto upkeep
goto upkeep
choice 1
goto upkeep
goto upkeep
[ASSERT]
UPKEEP
[PLAYER1]
graveyard:vapor snare
hand:*
library:darksteel citadel,millstone
[PLAYER2]
inplay:grizzly bears
hand:*
library:darksteel citadel
[END]
